:"9edcda96b824e08e2995a36275f7b024bd0ca9ef","tid":909463,"uid":7903,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"5d8b9e926a070b55aa6a6e7a8ce3e6e053d78833","tid":909463,"uid":150609,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T12:44:54.000Z","msg":"唱片商抵啦<br />\n以為自己夠料可以唔洗靠電視宣傳 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T02:08:10.000Z","msg":"個個都有份 打和<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa569af7cc0b351b948e41d50107018baf8939a5","tid":909463,"uid":48099,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T04:52:48.000Z","msg":"係老共"},{"pid":"0587a5084793653c2772595fb53a5a75f7830275","tid":909463,"uid":171594,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T05:49:17.000Z","msg":"唔使爭，全港歌迷都有份搞死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"097dc0c597a0fe5d827435c331ee9d3c79edf77e","tid":909463,"uid":76076,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T15:58:29.000Z","msg":"梗係TVB，節目製作方面，不論劇集和綜藝，都係一成不變，事事旦旦，每況愈下。例如劇集種類單一成日都爭產(仲要康雍乾模式)丶宫延爭寵丶警匪片等。劇情又好多時相類似。D爭產片永遠D舅父都衰人，警匪片永遠都有內鬼。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 劇集成出穿崩，現代交通工具穿越古裝劇。劇集成日抄中日韓劇，百鳥歸巢，洗鬼睇你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n。佢咁樣做，愈來愈少人睇TVB，觀眾咪對D香港藝人漸漸陌生，個娛樂圈咪愈縮愈細。<br />\n最過份仲要請魚x生呢D亢員做高層，成日比D不受歡迎的藝人( 鄭x暈、吳藥x)瘋狂出鏡，有潛質個D又唔去重用。香港電視節目質素<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n以前香港出到四大天王丶五虎將。現家香港娛樂圈都出唔到偶像巨星。見到咁，我都非常心up.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15ac1001f50b54dc0087e7a3396e1d23b4b19568","tid":909463,"uid":55960,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T16:06:52.000Z","msg":"你講娛樂圈既梗係TVB啦<br />\n你講樂壇我覺得TVB同所有唱片公司都有責任 （四大事件封殺, 用八卦唱衰對家）"},{"pid":"c5340ad473aa160c2c175d3d310214bce7c24d4d","tid":909463,"uid":113630,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8363585a7a768921bae773997576b187ca638cf5","tid":909463,"uid":34071,"like":5,"dislike":9,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T01:22:42.000Z","msg":"環球/商台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T16:54:04.000Z","msg":"環球係咪得罪太多人搞到d歌手少曝光，好似淨返麥當勞呢個宣傳渠道咁"},{"pid":"683a3d1d92db4bbf83fe23ed10a8b7dace9ec09d","tid":909463,"uid":193364,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0587a5084793653c2772595fb53a5a75f7830275","tid":909463,"uid":171594,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T05:49:17.000Z","msg":"唔使爭，全港歌迷都有份搞死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T17:09:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我諗係當年年經果批覺得老歌老土, 之後就紅左容袓兒依啲垃圾"},{"pid":"c7c3bfbfd5ad32965d524da5f929d5a61f7f3e09","tid":909463,"uid":193364,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"15ac1001f50b54dc0087e7a3396e1d23b4b19568","tid":909463,"uid":55960,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T16:06:52.000Z","msg":"你講娛樂圈既梗係TVB啦<br />\n你講樂壇我覺得TVB同所有唱片公司都有責任 （四大事件封殺, 用八卦唱衰對家）"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T17:11:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 樂壇唔係喺娛樂圈入面咩"},{"pid":"300a7dcc6a75251bd0c792fcb6771b71063a3811","tid":909463,"uid":193364,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T17:12:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔使爭，全港歌迷都有份搞死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我諗係當年年<span style=\"color: 